okato_ch" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Yoka Maizuru</strong></a> ， <a href="https://x.com/yoshibanakokoro" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Kokoro Yoshika</strong></a>和<a href="https://x.com/itopoid" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Itopoid</strong></a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1024x576.webp" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-jpg.webp 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" ></a></p><p>在Hakotore V中，您可以在镜子显示屏上与自己和Vtuber一起训练，您可以享受并轻松学习正确的形式。所有的VTUBER声音都是教练的记录。</p><p>此外，运动捕获摄像头检测到玩家的运动，VTUBER将其与您自己的步伐相匹配。菜单是由VTUBER完全监督的，VTUBER喜欢肌肉训练和训练教练，设计了一个菜单，从初学者到经验丰富的人，从有氧运动到高负荷训练。它还具有纪念性的照片拍摄功能，可以发布在SNS上，从而提供了VTUBER和粉丝可以在同一空间中愉快地一起锻炼的体验。</p><h2>参与VTUBER评论</h2><h3>初学者课程教练：Maizuru Yoka</h3><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-jpg.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-300x300.webp" alt="" width="300" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-254021" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-300x300.webp 300w, https://a